caption: I present to you a VACANT, TWO-FAMILY, in EAST Bergen Lafayette with 2 CAR PARKING on an EXTRA LARGE LOT! Yes, that is right - this is the property you have been waiting for. This home was built in 1993 and features 2 units, each having 3 bed 1 bath, a formal dining area, and laundry closets. Unit 1 has backdoor access to the massive yard and unit 2 has a balcony in the front of the property granting each unit the outdoor space everyone needs. This home also offers 2+ car parking, a brand new roof & windows, and super close proximity to Liberty State Park/LSP Light Rail. This property has electric heat- can be converted to central air - all separate utilities. Holla at cha girl. 🤜🏼🤛🏾 $949,000 $11,800 taxes!
